                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The gritblight forces disorienting visions of Ayrzul's Blistering Labyrinth into the minds of nearby creatures. All creatures in a @Template[type:cone|distance:60] take @Damage[7d12[mental]] damage with a @Check[type:will|dc:33] save. Creatures @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Blinded] by a gritblight's Labyrinthine Vision see only endless earthen tunnels in every direction.</p>\n<p>The gritblight can't use this ability again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is blinded for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is blinded permanently.</p>"
                },
